org.sql: SELECT 1 AS one FROM users INNER JOIN users_roles ON users_roles.user_id = users.id INNER JOIN roles ON roles.id = users_roles.role_id WHERE users_roles.role_id = "$1" LIMIT 1 OFFSET "$3"
